All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppInterface  
    Booking
    This Model class contains all information of a booking - including the name of the moviegoer, the email address, the date and time, the cineplex name, the cinema ID, the movie name, the seat booked, the price of the ticket, the age of the person, and the ticket ID.
    Cinema
    This Model class contains all information of a cinema - including its cineplex, the cinema ID, the type of the cinema (Platinum or Normal), the number of seats, the row number, and the column number.
    Cineplex
    This Model class contains all information of a cineplex - including its name and the number of cinemas.
    Comment  
    Holiday
    This Model class contains all information of a holiday - including its name and date.
    InputOutputController
    This Controller class handles input and also formats to desired output.
    Movie
    This Model class contains all information of a movie - including the title of the movie, the status, the duration, the director, the total sales, the age restriction, the rating, the synopsis, the cast members, and the base price, according to the movie type (Normal or Blockbuster).
    MovieBookingController
    This Controller class manages anything related to booking of showtimes made by the moviegoer.
    MoviegoerListMovieController
    This Controller class manages the display format of the list of movies for the moviegoer.
    Moviegoersearchcontroller
    This Controller class manages searching made by the moviegoer.
    MoviegoerView
    This View class displays the page for the moviegoer, and takes in input from the moviegoer and passes them to the Controller class for processing.
    Rating
    This Model class contains all information of a rating - including its rating iD, the movie title, the overall rating, and the reviews.
    readDatabaseTest  
    ShowTime
    This Model class contains all information of a showtime - including the name of the cineplex, the cinema ID, the movie name, the date and time, the row number, the column number, and the seating arrangement.
    Staff
    This Model class contains all information of a staff - including the staff's ID and the staff password for logging in purposes.
    StaffController
    This Controller class manages any changes made by the staff to any of the database.
    StaffListMovieController
    This Controller class manages the display format of the list of movies for the staff.
    StaffView
    This View class displays the page for the staff, and takes in input from the staff and passes them to the Controller class for processing.
    SuperController
    This Controller class is the parent class for all the controllers in the package.
